Recommends: software-properties-gtk | gnome-software
Description: GTK4 APT repository manager for Ubuntu/Xubuntu
 Repo Man is a graphical tool for managing third-party APT repositories.
 It provides an upgrade wizard that checks repository availability for a
 new Ubuntu release and updates Suites fields in one authenticated step.
 .
 Features include a pre-upgrade compatibility checker, GPG key management,
 add/remove repository dialogs, and save/restore of repository state across
 upgrades via .repoman config files.
